            <h3>Brought to you by</h3>
            <p>
              <a href="https://x.com/EthereumCzech" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">EthCzech Community</a>
            </p>
            <p>
              <a href="https://lu.ma/user/ethczech" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Lu.ma</a>
            </p>
